data.oai_dc:dc: The cluster assignments for strains by country of origin. Six clusters were found based on k-medoid clustering on the standard spectral density profiles of all strains (P < 0.05). The distribution across those clusters for strains sampled from 25 countries are shown for avian (a) and human (b) hosts. Four clusters were found using the normalized profiles (P < 0.05) and the distributions are shown for each country for avian (c) and human (d) hosts. Only countries with all seven strains sampled are represented.
